      "content": "Subject: Apology & Resolution for Your Espresso Machine Shipment Delay\n\nDear [Customer's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I wanted to personally reach out to you regarding your recent purchase of our espresso machine. We understand that the delay in your shipment has caused some inconvenience, and for that, we sincerely apologize.\n\nAs a valued customer, we want to make things right. We are currently working diligently to expedite the shipping process and have arranged for your espresso machine to arrive at your doorstep within the next two weeks. In recognition of the trouble this delay has caused, we would like to offer you a 15% discount on your next purchase with us. This discount will automatically be applied to your account and can be used at your convenience.\n\nWe truly appreciate your understanding and patience during this time. If you have any further questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to reach out to us. We are always here to help.\n\nWarm regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Your Contact Information]",
